(22, 1, '2017-07-17 22:11:43', '2017-07-17 22:11:43', '<h2><img class="wp-image-87 alignright" src="http://localhost:8080/wp/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/111111-300x290.jpg" alt="" width="304" height="293" />My name is Shiyar Ali  from Syria, I left Syria after the beginning of the war there in 2012, I got a bachelor''s degree from the National Technical University of Ukraine Ternopil city in 2017\r\nProgrammer, I know many programming languages, I have many projects in the Arduino board, speak five languages, participated in several scientific presentations to make my projects, my wish to become a professional programmer in the world, and making robots.</h2>\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nFor more information about me in Ukrainian language  you can also see this report :\r\n\r\nhttps://poglyad.te.ua/podii/strongznajomstvo-zblyzka-z-studentom-iz-syriyi-yakyj-navchayetsya-u-ternopilskomu-universytetistrong.html', 'About Me', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about', '', '', '2017-07-25 14:30:47', '2017-07-25 14:30:47', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/wp/?page_id=22', 0, 'page', '', 0),
